sentences: Hiroki Ino (猪野広樹, Ino Hiroki, born September 11, 1992) is a Japanese actor associated with Stardust Promotion's Section 2.
Ino debuted as an actor in 2009 and has notably appeared in the films Demolition Girl (2017) and Touken Ranbu (2019).
